      "pathways": [
        {
          "severity": "acute SCI with suspected instability",
          "criteria": "trauma + motor/sensory deficit or spinal tenderness with neurological symptoms",
          "treatment": "Immobilize: hard collar, blocks, spine board. Maintain MAP >85 with vasopressors. Avoid hypotension and hypoxia. Urgent MRI. Neurosurgical consultation. Consider methylprednisolone 30mg/kg bolus + 5.4mg/kg/hr x 23h (controversial). NGT for ileus. Foleys for retention."
